    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "phase4_title",
      "x": 1260,
      "y": 150,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "4. Vision, Guides &\nProcess Timers\n\n\u2022 Camera frame \u2192 Gemini Flash\n   vision assessment (4 tiers)\n\u2022 Gemini Image Gen creates\n   target-state guide photos\n\u2022 Priority queue (P0-P4)\n\u2022 Concurrent timer management\n\u2022 P1 conflict resolution",
      "originalText": "4. Vision, Guides &\nProcess Timers\n\n\u2022 Camera frame \u2192 Gemini Flash\n   vision assessment (4 tiers)\n\u2022 Gemini Image Gen creates\n   target-state guide photos\n\u2022 Priority queue (P0-P4)\n\u2022 Concurrent timer management\n\u2022 P1 conflict resolution",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
