    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "phase5_title",
      "x": 1690,
      "y": 150,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "5. Taste, Recovery &\nSession Complete\n\n\u2022 Taste diagnostic (5 dims)\n\u2022 \"Something's missing\" flow\n\u2022 Error recovery (4-step)\n\u2022 Completion wind-down\n\u2022 Memory confirmation gate\n\u2022 Preferences \u2192 Firestore\n\u2022 Analytics events emitted",
      "originalText": "5. Taste, Recovery &\nSession Complete\n\n\u2022 Taste diagnostic (5 dims)\n\u2022 \"Something's missing\" flow\n\u2022 Error recovery (4-step)\n\u2022 Completion wind-down\n\u2022 Memory confirmation gate\n\u2022 Preferences \u2192 Firestore\n\u2022 Analytics events emitted",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
